# Code owners for automatic review assignment
# See: https://docs.github.com/en/repositories/managing-your-repositorys-settings-and-features/customizing-your-repository/about-code-owners

# Default owners for everything in the repo
*       @platform-team

# Terraform files require platform team review
*.tf    @platform-team @infrastructure-lead

# GitHub Actions workflows require DevOps review
.github/    @devops-team @platform-team

# Production environment changes require additional review
environments/prod.tfvars    @platform-team @security-team @infrastructure-lead
